      skos:note "Structured retrospective memo with three H2 sections (What happened, The principle, How to hold it). Antithesis-heavy throughout (smokes vs. battery, mechanism vs. quality, appearance vs. control). Active voice dominant; imperative mood in How to hold it section. Jargon density low-moderate — product terms (smokes, battery, parity A/B, introspect gap-precision, token/OOM) used without definition, implying internal audience. Short punchy declaratives at principle peaks; longer analytical sentences in What happened section. Embedded blockquote from Scarlet elevates personal voice." ;
